    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="the kiss"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="kiss"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="love"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="sad"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    
                    <l>I hoped that he would love me,</l>
                    <l>And he has kissed my mouth,</l> 
                    <l> But I am like a stricken bird</l>
                    <l>That cannot reach the south. </l>
                    
                    <l>For though I know he loves me,</l> 
                    <l> To-night my heart is sad;</l> 
                    <l>His kiss was not so wonderful</l> 
                    <l>As all the dreams I had.</l>
                    
                    <l>Source: https://www.familyfriendpoems.com/poem/the-kiss-by-sara-teasdale</l>
                    
